        "tactics": [
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": "The fighter drinks her potions of <i>bull\u2019s strength</i>, <i>cat\u2019s grace</i>, and <i>barkskin</i>. If she\u2019s planning betrayal, a scheming fencer doesn\u2019t down her potions until just before her treachery."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": "The fighter uses Combat Expertise, hoping to wear her foes down. Every few rounds, she makes a disarm attempt with one of her attacks. She likes to gain a height advantage using her <i>slippers of spider climbing</i>."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Base Statistics",
                "text": "Without <i>bull\u2019s strength</i>, <i>cat\u2019s grace</i>, and <i>barkskin</i>, the fighter\u2019s statistics are <b>Init </b>+4; <b>AC </b>21, touch 14, flat-footed 17; <b>Ref </b>+8; <b>Melee</b><i>+1 rapier </i>+17/+12/+7 (1d6+6/15\u201320), mwk dagger +16/+11 (1d4+3/19\u201320); <b>Ranged </b>dagger +17 (1d4+3/19\u201320) or mwk composite longbow +17/+12/+7 (1d8+2/\u00d73); <b>Str </b>12, <b>Dex </b>19; <b>CMB </b>+12 (+14 disarm); <b>CMD </b>26 (28 vs. disarm); <b>Skills </b>Acrobatics +15, Climb +13."
            }
